# Transmute Framework Demo
# Usage: vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Start directly with the command
Type "/transmute:cast"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Pipeline output
Type "# ⚡ Transmute Framework v3.0.0 — Plan Casting Pipeline"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type "# "
Enter
Type "# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 0: Tech Stack Discovery    ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 1: BRD Generation          ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 2: PRD Generation          ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 2B: Spec Validation        ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 3: Scaffold Generation     ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 4: CLAUDE.md Verification  ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 5: Feature Implementation  ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 5B: Implementation Audit   ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 6A: Security Audit         ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 6B: Accessibility Audit    ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 6C: Performance Optimize   ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 6E: Code Refactoring       ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 6V: Visual Verification    ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 7: Deployment              ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 7V: Production Smoke Test  ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# │  Stage 7D: User Guide             ✅ Done   │"
Enter
Type "# └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type "# "
Enter
Type "# 🎉 Plan Casting complete! Your product is live."
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type "# 📦 Deployed to: https://my-saas-project.vercel.app"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
